        "Orphanet – Woodhouse-Sakati syndrome (https://www.google.com/search?q=Orphanet+Woodhouse-Sakati+syndrome): \"The cardinal features include hypogonadism, progressive hair loss affecting the scalp, eyebrows and eyelashes, insulin-dependent diabetes mellitus and extrapyramidal signs.\"",
