        "Wikipedia – Hurler syndrome (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hurler_syndrome): \"MPS I is a multisystem disorder affecting the skeletal system, eyes, heart, respiratory system, and central nervous system; corneal clouding, hepatosplenomegaly, and valvular heart disease are common in the severe (Hurler) form.\""
